t can be used to sanitize big data\nin a granular, application-specific manner by employing a suitable combination\nof diverse privacy-preserving algorithms to provide a proper balance between\nprivacy and utility.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Jul 2020 05:44:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Dec 2020 00:46:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 21 Apr 2021 13:30:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-22"}
